","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[25,520,5263,7641,21576],"comment_count":24,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"8 月 24 日消息，今日，Counterpoint Research 发布报告称，中国高端智能手机市场（批发价 400 美元约合人民币 2750 元及以上）的销量份额从 2021 年第二季度的 31% 微升至 2022 年第二季度的 33%。 IT之家了解到，报告指出，与整体市场的 14% 同比下降相比，高端市场的销量（包括准高端、高端和旗舰高端细分市场）仅下降了 10%。600-799 美元的高端（约合人民币 4100-5470 元）和 1000 美元及以上的旗舰高端（约合人民币 6850 元）的细分市场在 2022 年第二季度均录得增长。 数据显示，2022 年第二季度中国高端智能手机份额前六位分别为苹果（46%）、vivo（13%）、华为（11%）、荣耀（ 9%）、小米（ 8%）、OPPO（ 8%）。 Counterpoint 表示，2022 年第二季度，前六大 OEM 占据了整个高端市场 95% 的份额。与此同时，vivo 销量同比增长 91%，取代了华为首次在中国高端市场占据第二位。"},"attached_info":"Cj4Iks66xZm5s0YQAxoIODQ0NTE2MDAg9bmWmAYwGDjqAUAwcgk1NDk3NTQ5MDd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-1ed9d6849dd72df03fe64153c956afc3_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"49_1661548316.0478628","card_id":"Q_545817415","target":{"id":545817415,"title":"我父母似乎对电脑非常敏感，认为凡是碰电脑就是浪费时间，打两小时游戏和编程两小时都看成一样，如何反驳？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/545817415","type":"question","created":1659010202,"answer_count":54,"follower_count":86,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3132,7191,20403],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj0Iks66xZm5s0YQAxoIODM1NzU3MzQgmvmJlwYwBDhWQDFyCTU0NTgxNzQxNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]}],"description":{"time":"2022-08-27 05:11:56"}}